            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B9%BF%E4%B8%9C%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E8%A2%AB%E5%92%AC%E4%BC%A4%E5%90%8E%E6%8B%8E%E7%9D%80%E6%AF%92%E8%9B%87%E5%86%B2%E8%BF%9B%E5%8C%BB%E9%99%A2%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B9%BF%E4%B8%9C%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E8%A2%AB%E5%92%AC%E4%BC%A4%E5%90%8E%E6%8B%8E%E7%9D%80%E6%AF%92%E8%9B%87%E5%86%B2%E8%BF%9B%E5%8C%BB%E9%99%A2%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#广东女子被咬伤后拎着毒蛇冲进医院#</span></a>，是个狠人<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[喵喵]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_miao-c1b3d563bd.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】近日，龙岗一女子在分类废品时，被毒蛇咬伤，邻居帮忙把蛇打死后，家人竟然拎着蛇冲进了医院急诊科……经过医生鉴定，咬伤女子的蛇为竹叶青。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>医生提醒：不要捕捉或追打蛇，以免二次被咬👇🏻<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:5009696025673772" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">第一现场的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/6aac5feagy1hnjos7ez94j20u0140nbb.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/XvJPgVfygx08d7QFJEfe01041200hi8U0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1710191661&amp;ssig=ZXUukMuZ5m&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/VlmyS698gx08d7QF9N8Q01041200aW6X0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1710191661&amp;ssig=ptWxcxQVsE&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/UCkxSAlPgx08d7QEUUQw010412004XDI0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1710191661&amp;ssig=b47aAPKW7H&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A5009696025673772" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
