        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【🚶🏻♂️#三类人不宜长时间走路#】医生建议，普通人走路的步数，达到八千步就可以了，#日行一万步或可降低久坐危害# ，步速要控制在能说话不能唱歌的范围...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【🚶🏻♂️<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%89%E7%B1%BB%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9C%E9%95%BF%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E8%B5%B0%E8%B7%AF%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%89%E7%B1%BB%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9C%E9%95%BF%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E8%B5%B0%E8%B7%AF%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#三类人不宜长时间走路#</span></a>】医生建议，普通人走路的步数，达到八千步就可以了，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%97%A5%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%87%E6%AD%A5%E6%88%96%E5%8F%AF%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E%E4%B9%85%E5%9D%90%E5%8D%B1%E5%AE%B3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%97%A5%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%87%E6%AD%A5%E6%88%96%E5%8F%AF%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E%E4%B9%85%E5%9D%90%E5%8D%B1%E5%AE%B3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#日行一万步或可降低久坐危害#</span></a> ，步速要控制在能说话不能唱歌的范围；而冠心病、肥胖、下肢骨关节有疾病或损伤的人群，不适宜长时间走路👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6YrYaSd" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a> ]]></description>
