        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[[污]#那些用痔疮膏的人后来怎么样了#病情不算太重的情况下，比如排便时带鲜血，排完以后就不出血了；排便后有痔团从肛门脱出来，排便之后能自己缩回去等，#用痔...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[污]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_wu-374e5572e8.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E7%94%A8%E7%97%94%E7%96%AE%E8%86%8F%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E5%90%8E%E6%9D%A5%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E6%A0%B7%E4%BA%86%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E7%94%A8%E7%97%94%E7%96%AE%E8%86%8F%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E5%90%8E%E6%9D%A5%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E6%A0%B7%E4%BA%86%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#那些用痔疮膏的人后来怎么样了#</span></a><br><br>病情不算太重的情况下，比如排便时带鲜血，排完以后就不出血了；排便后有痔团从肛门脱出来，排便之后能自己缩回去等，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%94%A8%E7%97%94%E7%96%AE%E8%86%8F%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E6%B2%BB%E7%97%94%E7%96%AE%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%94%A8%E7%97%94%E7%96%AE%E8%86%8F%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E6%B2%BB%E7%97%94%E7%96%AE%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#用痔疮膏能不能治痔疮#</span></a>，可以遵医嘱，选择合适的药物进行治疗。<br><br>可一旦药物治疗效果不好时，比如痔核在肛门脱出严重、便血过多，肛周脓肿等，别再用痔疮药物凑合了，赶紧去医院，该手术还是得手术，万一是严重的混合感染，手术晚一天，术后就得花更长的时间恢复<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>(科普中国、健康广东）<img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnmx2l4xvqj20i50dnwfo.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnmx2l5405j20m80mkgor.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
